To download and build rainbow:

  git clone git://github.com/conanite/rainbow.git
  cd rainbow
  ant jar

Open welder.arc in welder:

  ARC_PATH=/PATH/TO/anarki/arc:./src/arc java -jar build/dist/rainbow/rainbow.jar -e '(welder "src/arc/rainbow/welder.arc")' 

Play tetris:

  ARC_PATH=/PATH/TO/anarki/arc:./src/arc java -jar build/dist/rainbow/rainbow.jar -e '(tetris)' 

Just open a REPL

  ARC_PATH=/PATH/TO/anarki/arc:./src/arc java -jar build/dist/rainbow/rainbow.jar
  
Command-line options:
  --strict-arc              # don't include anarki-compatible extensions
  -f file1 ... fileN        # evaluate each file
  -e '(arc axpr)'           # evaluate arc expr (after having evaluated -f, if specified)
  -args a b c               # sets "*argv*" in the arc environment to (a b c). This option, if present, must be specified last.

